title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 6 categories of Country on the x axis representing 4 groups: 2003, 2008, 2012, and 2015.
Averaging these 4 groups, the highest category is found for Country 30 to 39 with a mean value of 36.5.
The lowest category is observed at 65 and older that has a mean value of 8.0
showing a difference of 128.1% with the maximum value.

In case of 25 to 29, 2003 shows more dominance than any other Country and it has the lowest value in 65 and older. On the other hand, group 2008 is the second impactful group in this chart, and it's highest in case of 30 to 39 and has the minimum dominance for Country 65 and older.
